China to Raise Renewable-Power Charge 50%, Shanghai Daily Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-31T18:58:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/china-to-raise-renewable-power-charge-50-shanghai-daily-says.html
China will increase the surcharge on
electricity generated from renewable energy by 50 percent over
two years, Shanghai Daily said, citing the China Electricity
Regulatory Commission.   Grid operators may now charge 0.004 yuan per kilowatt hour
more for power from renewable sources than from conventional
thermal plants, the English-language newspaper said today.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  